//! gnosis-foil-control — small native control surface for the foil runtime.
//!
//! This is the first executable control-plane parity point with `gnosis-uring`.
//! It serves the foil runtime certificate, honest capability metadata, and a
//! uring-compatible 10-byte Flow/UDP listener for raw Aeon handoff frames.

